# Figma API Configuration
# Token expires based on your settings ($n days from creation)
# To generate: https://developers.figma.com/docs/rest-api/authentication/#access-tokens
FIGMA_API_TOKEN=your_figma_personal_access_token_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Get your Figma Personal Access Token:
#    - Log in to Figma
#    - Go to Settings > Security > Personal access tokens
#    - Generate new token with appropriate scopes
#    - Copy the token (you'll only see it once!)
# 3. Replace the placeholder above with your actual token
# 4. The MCP server will store this at: ~/.mcp-figma/config.json